channel.title: 'House 101' with DJ Logan Spencer
channel.description:
'House 101' is a live dance music set that is done weekly, every Friday. The goal is simple to describe, while also very challenging to execute, “I want to take the stigmas out of Dance music and provide something that’s approachable and enjoyable to anyone!”
With a vast knowledge in Progressive House music spanning over ten years, this guy has a lot to share!

item.description:

  • Ass Back Home (feat. Neon Hitch) [Ken Loi Extended Mix] - Gym Class Heroes
  • Dovregubben (Original Mix) - Zedd

  • Keep It Coming (Original Mix) - Starkillers and Nadia Ali
  • Alive (Paris FZ & Simo T Remix) - Dirty South & Thomas Gold Ft. Kate Elsworth
  • Toca's Miracle (Inpetto 2012 Update) - Fragma
  • One Touch Away (Club Mix) - Spencer and Hill

Welcome back, class is back in session... I hope everyone had a great holiday season and is ready for some great new EDM to start the new year with.  This week the playlist has a very progressive house (big room) feel to it....  all the big names (Kaskade, Afrojack, Guetta) with some new blood as well (Starkillers, Da Groove Doctors, and F*kkk Offf).  I hope you enjoy! -L.s
